{"title":"粉尸碎骨","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":12,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉尸碎骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国人手里的“卫星”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心一意想上天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成群的记者千里而来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“成功”的报道只待东风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它离地面没有多远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然“噼啪”的响了一声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“成功”突变成“失败”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啼不是来笑不成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫星上天不简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着吹嘘不成功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻想飞得倒挺高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跌下来丢尽“威风”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这“卫星”虽然粉尸碎骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没法为它的主子尽忠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的寿命只有两秒钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人们的笑谈里它永生。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}